OL,5,G2015 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FNetherlands v Japan (Kick-off
OL,7,     F9.00pm). Laura Woods presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group F match at
OL,9,     FDallas Stadium in the USA. There
OL,10,     Fhave been three previous meetings
OL,11,     Fbetween these nations, including a
OL,12,     Fgroup-stage match at the 2010
OL,13,     FWorld Cup in South Africa when a
OL,14,     Fsecond-half goal from Wesley
OL,15,     FSneijder was enough to give the
OL,16,     FDutch a 1-0 victory. Both teams
OL,17,     Fwent on to progress to the
OL,18,     Fknockout stage, and while the
OL,19,     FJapanese would bow out in the
OL,20,     Flast-16, Oranje made it all the
OL,21,     Fway to the final but fell short of
OL,22,     Fvictory in a 1-0 loss to Spain.
